வி.பெ. to be obtained  
to come to one  
to be rea lized  
found; to come into ones possession  
to turn to account  
அடைய. with the agent in the dative  
and the object in the nomi nativeas எனக்கொருபுஸ்்தகங்கிடைத்தது; lit. a book has come to me; i.e. i have obtained a book  
2. to encounter  
to be confronted withas warriors; to oppose  
எதிர்க்க. in the first sense  
the verb is commonly used in the neuter gender. எனக்குப்பாக்கியங்கிடைத்தது. i have become rich or happy. i have had prosperity. வழுக்கிவிழுகையில் ஊன்றுகோல்போல் நீ கிடைத் தாயே. you have offered yourself to me as a propas a walkingstick to one who slips and is ready to fall  
